      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ASTON POLICY (6) was in the placings last time but prior to that she posted a superb 25.25 win over 450m at Shepparton. Hard to top on the time from two back. VICTORY YACHT (3) was big odds last time but gave a huge sight after a fast early split and ran away with a 4 length win at Sandown over 515m in 29.66. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Will go close again if runs up to latest. PAW GELDOFF (4) struggled in tougher grade last start after settling off pace at Sandown, but prior to that won by 2.75 lengths at Sandown (29.95) beating Ready One in a Grade 5 on March 26. Has ability and can atone. ROWDY BOY (7) should be thereabouts despite an unplaced run here most recently.",
